        <Parent_String>Mainland Greek pottery styles [300107002], Greek pottery styles [300020113], Aegean pottery styles [300020105], Aegean styles [300106921], Aegean [300020059], Mediterranean (Early Western World) [300020058], Early Western World [300019255], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
